91
00:09:44,379 --> 00:09:48,870
SPEAKER_03: Mr. Long'er says
if you're busy he'll take a rain check.

92
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:51,570
SPEAKER_03: No, have him wait. I'll be right there.

93
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,779
SPEAKER_03: This is the last time, okay? I promise.

94
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:58,480
SPEAKER_03: Go home, go.

95
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,590
SPEAKER_03: It's settled.

222
00:23:49,690 --> 00:23:51,420
SPEAKER_03: Life won't be easy.

280
00:32:06,150 --> 00:32:07,549
SPEAKER_03: The wounded.

283
00:32:13,490 --> 00:32:14,980
SPEAKER_03: No one's left.

284
00:32:16,089 --> 00:32:19,119
SPEAKER_03: Must be tens of thousands
of us trapped here.

291
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:53,089
SPEAKER_03: Lao Quan, have a drink.

292
00:32:58,029 --> 00:32:59,359
SPEAKER_03: It really is booze!

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_03: So, no running?

319
00:34:48,039 --> 00:34:49,940
SPEAKER_03: This will do the trick?

324
00:35:19,739 --> 00:35:22,940
SPEAKER_03: - The attack hasn't started.
- Let's put them down.

673
01:18:59,500 --> 01:19:01,159
SPEAKER_03: I meant to call...

674
01:19:02,199 --> 01:19:03,930
SPEAKER_03: after I settled in.

675
01:19:06,699 --> 01:19:07,930
SPEAKER_03: Fugui...

676
01:19:09,710 --> 01:19:11,699
SPEAKER_03: how could it be your son?

686
01:19:57,550 --> 01:19:59,489
SPEAKER_03: Take this for now.

687
01:20:02,159 --> 01:20:03,520
SPEAKER_03: It's money.

688
01:20:04,859 --> 01:20:07,520
SPEAKER_03: Tell me what else I can do.

702
01:20:56,909 --> 01:20:58,539
SPEAKER_03: I owe you a life.

703
01:21:01,149 --> 01:21:02,739
SPEAKER_03: I will remember.

873
01:37:43,579 --> 01:37:45,880
SPEAKER_03: Congratulations on Fengxia's wedding.

874
01:37:46,289 --> 01:37:48,760
SPEAKER_03: - When did you get here?
- A while ago.

875
01:37:49,090 --> 01:37:52,149
SPEAKER_03: But there were so many people,
I didn't come in.

891
01:39:05,899 --> 01:39:07,270
SPEAKER_03: Never mind.

892
01:39:09,939 --> 01:39:12,739
SPEAKER_03: Jiazhen, I know you don't want to see me.

893
01:39:13,170 --> 01:39:15,800
SPEAKER_03: I'll leave my gift here and be gone.

950
01:44:06,270 --> 01:44:07,430
SPEAKER_03: Fugui!

951
01:44:11,369 --> 01:44:12,770
SPEAKER_03: Who's there?

952
01:44:12,840 --> 01:44:14,210
SPEAKER_03: Chunsheng.

953
01:44:15,539 --> 01:44:16,640
SPEAKER_03: Who?

954
01:44:16,710 --> 01:44:18,039
SPEAKER_03: Chunsheng.

955
01:44:23,149 --> 01:44:24,779
SPEAKER_03: What do you want?

956
01:44:26,949 --> 01:44:28,850
SPEAKER_03: Come out for a second.

958
01:44:33,760 --> 01:44:35,819
SPEAKER_03: It'll just take a minute.

960
01:45:10,100 --> 01:45:11,329
SPEAKER_03: Fugui...

961
01:45:12,329 --> 01:45:15,060
SPEAKER_03: I've always felt terrible about Youqing.

962
01:45:17,340 --> 01:45:21,300
SPEAKER_03: I've often tried to give you money.
You'd never accept it.

963
01:45:23,180 --> 01:45:26,310
SPEAKER_03: It's all in this account. Take it.

964
01:45:29,649 --> 01:45:31,350
SPEAKER_03: You came for this?

965
01:45:33,390 --> 01:45:34,819
SPEAKER_03: Take this...

966
01:45:36,220 --> 01:45:38,420
SPEAKER_03: and my heart will be at ease.

967
01:45:40,859 --> 01:45:43,060
SPEAKER_03: All my debts will have been paid.

974
01:46:01,279 --> 01:46:02,340
SPEAKER_03: No.

975
01:46:03,720 --> 01:46:05,979
SPEAKER_03: I just got an official notice.

990
01:47:11,619 --> 01:47:13,449
SPEAKER_03: I don't think I can.

995
01:47:30,100 --> 01:47:32,039
SPEAKER_03: I snuck out just now...

996
01:47:32,109 --> 01:47:33,899
SPEAKER_03: and better get back.

997
01:47:41,380 --> 01:47:44,350
SPEAKER_03: Chunsheng, remember...

